detail.name: Golden Great Ape Son Goku
detail.effect: [When Attacking] If your Leader is <Son Goku : GT>, look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 <Great Ape Who Gained Intelligence> and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of its owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: 黄金大猿孫悟空
detail.effect: 【アタック時】自分のリーダーが「孫悟空：GT」の場合、自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、「理性を持った大猿」1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
